Thanks... With the following header hash function it was able to process all blocks:
```
    @classmethod
    def header_hash(cls, header):
        '''
        Given a header return the hash for CivX.
        Need to download `x13_hash` module
        Source code: https://github.com/MaruCoinOfficial/x13-hash"
        '''
        import x13_hash
        version, = util.unpack_le_uint32_from(header)

        if version > 2:
            return double_sha256(header)
        else:
            return x13_hash.getPoWHash(header)
```
